headline: Ulta Beauty: More Headwinds Ahead As Growth Stalls & Balance Sheet Deteriorates
summary: ULTA continues to underperform in comparable/ net sales performance compared to ELF and LVMH owned Sephora, despite the recently raised FY2024 guidance.
